                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the commissioner and his family members; group of lines on the incipit page of the text, alternating with black lines; incipit of each section of the text; two initial lines of each section of the text; names of Hebrew letters in Ps. 118 (e.g., fols. 44ra, 46vb, 48ra); elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; some other words, e.g., ṣällǝyu (e.g., fols. 19va, 20va, 21rb),  wä-kaʿǝbä (e.g., fols. 22vb, 23va), kәśtät (e.g., fols. 41ra, 64rb, 71ra).</rubric>
